descriptionHtml:
[font=Georgia][color=#b4a7d6][size=5][b]Description[/b][/size][/color]


[/font][size=2]Neo's Tina Conversion for UNPB
Original mod from [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/oblivion/mods/40329/?]Oblivion[/url] by Neovinci aka Meister
and Converted to [url=http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/27308/?]Skyrim[/url] by Nausicaa

a bit of changes, not much and tried to get the Tail moving
so it need HDT Physics Extension to work properly
any other accessories for the Red set, are combined with the Gloves and Boots
also the Gloves for Black set were combined with the Body, and it will use default Femalehand_.nif

all items are craftable at Forge under Daedric [i](if you use old crafting UI/SkyUI away)[/i]
dont forget about NiO High Heels, for ECE/Vanilla users you need Netimmerse Override

equipment list :
Tina (Black) Body
Tina (Black) Boots
Tina (Black) LegBelt [color=#00ffff]= slot 53[/color]
Tina (Black) Stocking [color=#00ffff]= slot 54[/color]
Tina (Black) Tail [color=#00ffff]= slot 40[/color]

Tina (Red) Body
Tina (Red) Boots
Tina (Red) Gloves

[/size][font=Georgia][color=#e06666][b]

[size=5]Required[/size]

[/b][/color][/font][font=Comic Sans MS][size=3]HDT Physics Extension
XPMSE
RaceMenu/Netimmerse Override[/size][/font]

[b]

[color=#93c47d][font=Georgia][size=5]Credits
[/size][/font]and thanks to..
[font=Comic Sans MS][size=3]
[/size][/font][/color][/b][font=Comic Sans MS][size=3]Neovinci for Neo's Tina
Nausicaa for converting it to skyrim
Caliente and ousnius for Bodyslide and outfit Studio
dimon99, xp32 and MTM for UNPB body
optioq for physic tail boneweight and XML
halofarm for high poly UNP hand

[/size][/font]
